    <span rel="sioc:reply_of" resource="/articles/2014/08/Amazon-v-Hatchette-Everyone-Wrong-Me" class="rdf-meta"></span><div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden view-mode-full"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p>I didn't realize that. So under that legislation you wouldn't even have to black-box it? You could just tear it apart directly? That's interesting.</p>
</div></div></div>  </div>

      <div class="user-signature"><p>--<br /><em>Writer, former musician, occasional cartoonist, and noted authority on his own opinions.</em></p>
</div>
  
      <nav class="clearfix"><ul class="links inline"><li class="comment-reply first last"><a href="/comment/reply/3619/23914">reply</a></li></ul></nav>
  
