          </header>
  
      <footer class="submitted">
            <p class="author-datetime"><span property="dc:date dc:created" content="2014-08-11T17:28:31-05:00" datatype="xsd:dateTime" rel="sioc:has_creator">Submitted by <span class="username" xml:lang="" typeof="sioc:UserAccount" property="foaf:name" datatype="">Scott Robertson (not verified)</span> on <time datetime="2014-08-11T17:28:31Z" pubdate="pubdate"><span class="date-time">Mon, 2014-08-11 17:28</span></time></span></p>
